e also shared sessions' commitment to "confirming federal judges who follow the law and who do not legislate from the bench and his focus on reducing america's dependence on foreign oil."</p><p>(candidate last) is scheduled to campaign in georgia on sunday, february 3, 2008 and in tennessee and arkansas on monday, february 4.</p></span>



